    $lang['about-2'] = 'Vestamatic + CRE meets the needs of today’s buildings and future developments with in-house electronic design, manufacture and firmware development, scalable engineering solutions and expert support. With our focus on specification, commissioning and maintenance of contract and hospitality shading automation, we design, create and deliver one-stop-shop solutions with our partners. ';
